OL,3,C'Predator' abused boys while working
OL,4,Cat children's hospital
OL,6,FA sexual predator who "abused his
OL,7,Fpower" to assault boys while working
OL,8,Fat a children's hospital has been
OL,9,Fjailed for almost a quarter of a
OL,10,Fdecade.
OL,12,FGraham Goodchild, 82, worked as a
OL,13,Fnight superintendent at Alder Hey in
OL,14,FLiverpool during the 1960s and early
OL,15,F1970s.
OL,17,FIn that time, he subjected four boys
OL,18,Fto "truly horrific" assaults, with one
OL,19,Fvictim abused within the hospital
OL,20,Fitself.
