OL,6,FThe rest of Goodchild's catalog of
OL,7,Fcrimes occurred within parks, the
OL,8,Fhomes of the victims, and his own
OL,9,Fhouse on Merseyside.
OL,11,FThe pensioner denied the offences but,
OL,12,Ffollowing a trial at Liverpool Crown
OL,13,FCourt, he was found guilty of 17
OL,14,Fcounts of sexual assault and an
OL,15,Fattempted sexual assault.
OL,17,FGoodchild, of Firtree Way, in
OL,18,FSouthampton, will serve a minimum of
OL,19,F24 years in prison for the historic
OL,20,Foffences, and will be required to sign
OL,21,Fthe sex offender register for life.
