OL,6,FDetective Constable Jason Banks, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation, said:
OL,8,F"Goodchild is clearly a predator and
OL,9,Fused his position of trust to carry
OL,10,Fout appalling and despicable offences
OL,11,Fagainst young children.
OL,13,F"The level of offending in this case
OL,14,Fand the acts he subjected his victims
OL,15,Fto were truly horrific."
