OL,6,FSpecially Trained Officer, Jill
OL,7,FBurnett, who supported the victims
OL,8,Fthroughout the investigation, added:
OL,9,F"I hope this also encourages others
OL,10,Fwho might have been subjected to
OL,11,Finstances of historical abuse to come
OL,12,Fforward because no time is a barrier
OL,13,Fto reporting offences.
OL,15,F"They will get the support and advice
OL,16,Fthey need to help them come to terms
OL,17,Fwith their ordeal, and if they so
OL,18,Fwish, put their abuser before the
OL,19,Fcourts."
